      "content": "                         YNYPledge: A New Era for Female Entrepreneurship in York & North Yorkshire | Enterprise Works at the University of York posted on the topic | LinkedIn              \n\n  \n\nAgree & Join LinkedIn\n\nBy clicking Continue to join or sign in, you agree to LinkedIn’s [User Agreement](/legal/user-agreement?trk=linkedin-tc_auth-button_user-agreement), [Privacy Policy](/legal/privacy-policy?trk=linkedin-tc_auth-button_privacy-policy), and [Cookie Policy](/legal/cookie-policy?trk=linkedin-tc_auth-button_cookie-policy).\n\n[Skip to main content](#main-content)\n\n[LinkedIn](/?trk=public_post_nav-header-logo)\n\n*   [Top Content](https://www.linkedin.com/top-content?trk=public_post_guest_nav_menu_topContent)\n*   [People](https://www.linkedin.com/pub/dir/+/+?trk=public_post_guest_nav_menu_people)\n*   [Learning](https://www.linkedin.com/learning/search?trk=public_post_guest_nav_menu_learning)\n*   [Jobs](https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/search?trk=public_post_guest_nav_menu_jobs)\n*   [Games](https://www.linkedin.com/games?trk=public_post_guest_nav_menu_games)\n*   [Get the app](ms-windows-store://pdp/?ProductId=9WZDNCRFJ4Q7&mode=mini&cid=guest_nav_upsell&trk=public_post_guest_nav_menu_windows)\n\n[Sign in](https://www.linkedin.com/login?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww%2Elinkedin%2Ecom%2Fposts%2Fenterprise-works-at-the-university-of-york_new-era-for-female-entrepreneurship-in-york-activity-7240024268216889344-WGT-&fromSignIn=true&trk=public_post_nav-header-signin) [Join now](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww%2Elinkedin%2Ecom%2Fposts%2Fenterprise-works-at-the-university-of-york_new-era-for-female-entrepreneurship-in-york-activity-7240024268216889344-WGT-&trk=public_post_nav-header-join) [](https://www.linkedin.com/login?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww%2Elinkedin%2Ecom%2Fposts%2Fenterprise-works-at-the-university-of-york_new-era-for-female-entrepreneurship-in-york-activity-7240024268216889344-WGT-&fromSignIn=true&trk=public_post_nav-header-signin)\n\n# YNYPledge: A New Era for Female Entrepreneurship in York & North Yorkshire\n\nThis title was summarized by AI from the post below.\n\n [](https://uk.linkedin.com/showcase/enterprise-works-at-the-university-of-york/?trk=public_post_feed-actor-image)\n\n[Enterprise Works at the University of York](https://uk.linkedin.com/showcase/enterprise-works-at-the-university-of-york/?trk=public_post_feed-actor-name)\n\n1,605 followers\n\n1y\n\n*   [Report this post](/uas/login?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fenterprise-works-at-the-university-of-york_new-era-for-female-entrepreneurship-in-york-activity-7240024268216889344-WGT-&trk=public_post_ellipsis-menu-semaphore-sign-in-redirect&guestReportContentType=POST&_f=guest-reporting)\n\nA New Era for Female Entrepreneurship in York & North Yorkshire Our region has the potential to create up to 165,000 jobs and add £2.6 billion to GVA by investing in female entrepreneurs. However, our research shows that despite these opportunities, women in business still face significant barriers – from entrenched social norms to challenges accessing funding and support. We’re calling on organisations, leaders, and policymakers to take action by: - Sharing success stories of female entrepreneurs - Offering tailored support - Promoting supplier diversity - Implementing inclusive work policies - Advocating for women-owned businesses Women in business, we need your voices to continue driving this change. Let's work together to build a future of equity, empowerment, and growth for all in York & North Yorkshire. Show your support and sign the pledge today - [https://bit.ly/3zGKCDp](https://www.linkedin.com/redir/redirect?url=https%3A%2F%2Fbit%2Ely%2F3zGKCDp&urlhash=PL4Y&trk=public_post-text) [#WomenInBusiness](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Fwomeninbusiness&trk=public_post-text) [#SupportFemaleEntrepreneurs](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Fsupportfemaleentrepreneurs&trk=public_post-text) [#InclusiveGrowth](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Finclusivegrowth&trk=public_post-text) [#YNYPledge](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Fynypledge&trk=public_post-text)\n\n[\n\nNew Era for Female entrepreneurship in York and North Yorkshire Pledge york.ac.uk\n\n\n\n](https://www.linkedin.com/redir/redirect?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww%2Eyork%2Eac%2Euk%2Fenterprise-works%2Fa-new-era-for-female-entrepreneurship%2Fnew-era-pledge%2F&urlhash=GIs4&trk=public_post_feed-article-content)\n\n  [12](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww%2Elinkedin%2Ecom%2Fposts%2Fenterprise-works-at-the-university-of-york_new-era-for-female-entrepreneurship-in-york-activity-7240024268216889344-WGT-&trk=public_post_social-actions-reactions)\n\n[Like](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww%2Elinkedin%2Ecom%2Fposts%2Fenterprise-works-at-the-university-of-york_new-era-for-female-entrepreneurship-in-york-activity-7240024268216889344-WGT-&trk=public_post_like-cta) [Comment](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww%2Elinkedin%2Ecom%2Fposts%2Fenterprise-works-at-the-university-of-york_new-era-for-female-entrepreneurship-in-york-activity-7240024268216889344-WGT-&trk=public_post_comment-cta)\n\nShare\n\n*   Copy\n*   LinkedIn\n*   Facebook\n*   X\n\nTo view or add a comment, [sign in](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww%2Elinkedin%2Ecom%2Fposts%2Fenterprise-works-at-the-university-of-york_new-era-for-female-entrepreneurship-in-york-activity-7240024268216889344-WGT-&trk=public_post_feed-cta-banner-cta)\n\n![](https://media.licdn.com/dms/