k?trk=public_post_feed-actor-name)\n    \n    531 followers\n    \n    4mo\n    \n    *   [Report this post](https://www.linkedin.com/uas/login?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fiiitm-k_womenentrepreneurship-startupecosystem-activity-7394589223028391936-e2F5&trk=public_post_ellipsis-menu-semaphore-sign-in-redirect&guestReportContentType=POST&_f=guest-reporting)\n    \n    Launch of the Lift Off Cohort for Women Entrepreneurs With the objective of empowering women-led enterprises, we are delighted to announce the launch of the Lift Off Cohort, an exclusive 14-week program designed to support 15 women entrepreneurs in scaling up their ventures. Organized in association with WIIT and the Wadhwani Foundation, this initiative aims to provide structured mentoring and guidance to help entrepreneurs identify challenges, strengthen their business models, and accelerate growth. The program was inaugurated today, with Ms. Vidhu Vincent, renowned film director, delivering an inspiring address that motivated the participants to pursue their entrepreneurial goals with renewed confidence and purpose. We extend our sincere appreciation to Ms. Sanghamitra, the Wadhwani Foundation, and the WIIT team for their invaluable support in realizing this initiative. Together, we continue our commitment to nurturing women entrepreneurs and strengthening the innovation ecosystem. [#WomenEntrepreneurship](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Fwomenentrepreneurship&trk=public_post-text) [#StartupEcosystem](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Fstartupecosystem&trk=public_post-text) [#WadhwaniFoundation](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Fwadhwanifoundation&trk=public_post-text) [#WIIT](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Fwiit&trk=public_post-text) [#LiftOffCohort](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Fliftoffcohort&trk=public_post-text) [#Innovation](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Finnovation&trk=public_post-text) [#Empowerment](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Fempowerment&trk=public_post-text) [#Entrepreneurship](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Fentrepreneurship&trk=public_post-text) [#WomenInBusiness](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Fwomeninbusiness&trk=public_post-text)\n    \n    *    \n    \n     [7](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fiiitm-k_womenentrepreneurship-startupecosystem-activity-7394589223028391936-e2F5&trk=public_post_social-actions-reactions)\n    \n    [Like](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fiiitm-k_womenentrepreneurship-startupecosystem-activity-7394589223028391936-e2F5&trk=public_post_like-cta) [Comment](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fiiitm-k_womenentrepreneurship-startupecosystem-activity-7394589223028391936-e2F5&trk=public_post_comment-cta)\n    \n    Share\n    \n    *   Copy\n    *   LinkedIn\n    *   Facebook\n    *   X\n    \n    To view or add a comment, [sign in](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fiiitm-k_womenentrepreneurship-startupecosystem-activity-7394589223028391936-e2F5&trk=public_post_feed-cta-banner-cta)\n    \n*   [](https://www.linkedin.com/posts/isocialenterprise_ise-socialenterpr