text) [Legacy WM](https://uk.linkedin.com/company/legacy-wm?trk=public_post-text)\n    \n    …more\n    \n      [15](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fisocialenterprise_ise-socialenterprise-entrepreneurship-activity-7386344272419106816-fKPn&trk=public_post_social-actions-reactions) [4 Comments](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fisocialenterprise_ise-socialenterprise-entrepreneurship-activity-7386344272419106816-fKPn&trk=public_post_social-actions-comments)\n    \n    [Like](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fisocialenterprise_ise-socialenterprise-entrepreneurship-activity-7386344272419106816-fKPn&trk=public_post_like-cta) [Comment](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fisocialenterprise_ise-socialenterprise-entrepreneurship-activity-7386344272419106816-fKPn&trk=public_post_comment-cta)\n    \n    Share\n    \n    *   Copy\n    *   LinkedIn\n    *   Facebook\n    *   X\n    \n    To view or add a comment, [sign in](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fisocialenterprise_ise-socialenterprise-entrepreneurship-activity-7386344272419106816-fKPn&trk=public_post_feed-cta-banner-cta)\n    \n*   [](https://www.linkedin.com/posts/bwbn_minister-valdez-announces-189-million-investment-activity-7386883193028665346-NQ9f)\n    \n     [](https://ca.linkedin.com/company/bwbn?trk=public_post_feed-actor-image)\n    \n    [Black Women Business Network](https://ca.linkedin.com/company/bwbn?trk=public_post_feed-actor-name)\n    \n    2,087 followers\n    \n    5mo Edited\n    \n    *   [Report this post](https://www.linkedin.com/uas/login?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fbwbn_minister-valdez-announces-189-million-investment-activity-7386883193028665346-NQ9f&trk=public_post_ellipsis-menu-semaphore-sign-in-redirect&guestReportContentType=POST&_f=guest-reporting)\n    \n    ✨ Big news for Black entrepreneurs in Canada! Minister Valdez has announced a $189 million investment to help Black entrepreneurs start up, scale up, and grow Canada’s economy. This funding strengthens opportunities for Black-owned businesses and empowers innovators across the country- especially Black women entrepreneurs leading with impact. 💪🏾 🔗 Read more: [https://lnkd.in/gKfr5jxw](https://www.linkedin.com/redir/redirect?url=https%3A%2F%2Flnkd%2Ein%2FgKfr5jxw&urlhash=P6u2&trk=public_post-text) [#BlackExcellence](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Fblackexcellence&trk=public_post-text) [#BlackWomenInBusiness](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Fblackwomeninbusiness&trk=public_post-text) [#Entrepreneurship](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Fentrepreneurship&trk=public_post-text) [#InclusiveEconomy](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Finclusiveeconomy&trk=public_post-text) [#Leadership](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Fleadership&trk=public_post-text) [#CommunityGrowth](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Fcommunitygrowth&trk=public_post-text)\n    \n    [\n    \n    Minister Valdez announces $189 million investment to help Black entrepreneurs start up, scale up, and build Canada’s economy canada.ca\n    \n    \n    \n    ](https://www.linkedin.com/redir/redirect?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww%2Ecanada%2Eca%2Fen%2Finnovation-science-economic-development%2Fnews%2F2025%2F10%2Fminister-valdez-announces-189-million-investment-to-help-black-entrepreneurs-start-up-scale-up-and-build-canadas-economy%2Ehtml&urlhash=LLIo&trk=public_post_feed-article-content)\n    \n     [7](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fbwbn_minister-valdez-announces-189-million-investment-activity-7386883193028665346-NQ9f&trk=public_post_social-actions-reactions)\n    \n    [Like](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fbwbn_minister-valdez-announces-189-million-investment-activity-7386883193028665346-NQ9f&trk=public_post_like-cta) [Comment](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fbwbn_minister-valdez-announces-189-million-investment-activity-7386883193028665346-NQ9f&trk=public_post_comment-cta)\n    \n    Share\n    \n    *   Copy\n    *   LinkedIn\n    *   Facebook\n    *   X\n    \n    To view or add a comment, [sign in](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fbwbn_minister-valdez-announces-189-million-investment-activity-7386883193028665346-NQ9f&trk=public_post_feed-cta-banner-cta)\n    \n*   [](https://www.linkedin.com/posts/breakthrough-labs_the-uk-governments-female-entrepreneurship-activity-7395018934774636544-yzAa)\n    \n     [](https://uk.linkedin.com/company/breakthrough-labs?trk=public_post_feed-actor-image)\n    \n    [Breakthrough Labs](https://uk.linkedin.com/company/breakthrough-labs?trk=public_post_feed-actor-name)\n    \n    1,297 followers\n    \n    4mo\n    \n    *   [Report this post](https://www.linkedin.com/uas/login?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fbreakthrough-labs_the-uk-governments-female-entrepreneurship-activity-7395018934774636544-yzAa&trk=public_post_ellipsis-menu-semaphore-sign-in-redirect&guestReportContentType=POST&_f=guest-reporting)\n    \n    The UK government's Female Entrepreneurship report, released last month, opened with this: \"Female entrepreneurs face significant disadvantages in accessing finance, investment networks, and support systems.\" It's damning. But necessary. The data tells the story: in some cases, funding for women entrepreneurs is worse than previous years. At best, it's stagnant. We're not moving the needle. The report makes bold recommendations—from mandatory VC reporting to dedicated investment schemes. But two recommendations particularly resonated with us: the need for more networks outside London and more accelerators specifically for female founders. This is exactly what we've built at Breakthrough Labs. We're proud to be part of the solution—creating the support systems, networks, and safe spaces that women tech founders need to get their businesses to market and in front of investors. From pitch practices where you can face the tough questions in a supportive environment, to connections with investors who understand deep tech, we're here to change the narrative. The data hasn't changed enough. But we're committed to changing that, one founder at a time. Tag a female founder who might benefit from our community! 👇\n    \n    *    \n    \n     [1](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fbreakthrough-labs_the-uk-governments-female-entrepreneurship-activity-7395018934774636544-yzAa&trk=public_post_social-actions-reactions)\n    \n    [Like](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fbreakthrough-labs_the-uk-governments-female-entrepreneurship-activity-7395018934774636544-yzAa&trk=public_post_like-cta) [Comment](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fbreakthrough-labs_the-uk-governments-female-entrepreneurship-activity-7395018934774636544-yzAa&trk=public_post_comment-cta)\n    \n    Share\n    \n    *   Copy\n    *   LinkedIn\n    *   Facebook\n    *   X\n    \n    To view