      "content": "      Female Advisory Board launches peer group to accelerate growth of Yorkshire businesses | Startups Magazine                                                          \n\n[![Startups Magazine](https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/logo-home.jpg)](https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/ \"Startups Magazine\")\n\nNow Reading\n\n###### Female Advisory Board launches peer group to accelerate growth of Yorkshire businesses\n\n[0](https://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/article-female-advisory-board-launches-peer-group-accelerate-growth-yorkshire-businesses)\n\n[](https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=Female%20Advisory%20Board%20launches%20peer%20group%20to%20accelerate%20growth%20of%20Yorkshire%20businesses&via=TheStartupsMag&url=https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/article-female-advisory-board-launches-peer-group-accelerate-growth-yorkshire-businesses)\n\n[](https://www.linkedin.com/cws/share?url=https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/article-female-advisory-board-launches-peer-group-accelerate-growth-yorkshire-businesses)\n\n[](https://wa.me/?text=Female%20Advisory%20Board%20launches%20peer%20group%20to%20accelerate%20growth%20of%20Yorkshire%20businesses%20https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/article-female-advisory-board-launches-peer-group-accelerate-growth-yorkshire-businesses)\n\n[![Startups Magazine](https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/logo-home.jpg)](https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/ \"Startups Magazine\")\n\n[![Subscribe today](https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/stamp_new@2x.png)](/subscribe/)\n\n[![Startups Magazine](https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/logo-home.jpg)](https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/ \"Startups Magazine\")\n\n[\n\nTwitter\n\n\n\n](https://twitter.com/TheStartupsMag)\n\n[\n\nInstagram\n\n\n\n](https://instagram.com/startupsmagazine)\n\n[\n\nYoutube\n\n\n\n](https://youtube.com/channel/UCccztX35OPFsyKBfPV-pB9Q)\n\n[\n\nLinkedin\n\n\n\n](https://www.linkedin.com/company/startups-magazine)\n\n*   [Articles](https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/articles)\n    *   [Brand](https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/articles/brand)\n    *   [Diversity](https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/articles/diversity)\n    *   [Features](https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/articles/features)\n    *   [Funding](https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/articles/funding)\n    *   [HR](https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/articles/hr)\n    *   [Life](https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/articles/life)\n    *   [News](https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/articles/news)\n    *   [Startups](https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/articles/startups)\n*   [Events](/events/)\n*   [Podcasts](https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/podcasts)\n*   [Magazines](https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/magazines)\n*   [Videos](https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/video)\n*   [Subscribe](https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/subscribe)\n*   [Login](https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/login)\n\n*   Follow\n    *   [\n        \n        Twitter\n        \n        \n        \n        ](https://twitter.com/TheStartupsMag)\n        \n        [\n        \n        Instagram\n        \n        \n        \n        ](https://instagram.com/startupsmagazine)\n        \n        [\n        \n        Youtube\n        \n        \n        \n        ](https://youtube.com/channel/UCccztX35OPFsyKBfPV-pB9Q)\n        \n        [\n        \n        Linkedin\n        \n        \n        \n        ](https://www.linkedin.com/company/startups-magazine)\n        \n    *   #### Sign Up to Our Newsletter\n        \n        Get notified about exclusive offers every week!\n        \n         SIGN UP\n        \n         I would like to receive news and special offers.\n        \n\n[News](https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/articles/news)\n\n# Female Advisory Board launches peer group to accelerate growth of Yorkshire businesses\n\n![](https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Anna-Wood-150x150.jpeg)\n\n_by_ [Anna Wood](https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/author/anna-wood \"Posts by Anna Wood\")\n\nFebruary 3, 2025\n\n![](https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Female-Advisory-Board-launches-peer-group-to-accelerate-growth-of-Yorkshire-businesses.png)\n\n![](https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Anna-Wood-150x150.jpeg)\n\n[Anna Wood](https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/author/anna-wood)\n\nAnna Wood is the Editor of Startups Magazine. She joined…\n\n0 Shares\n\n[0](https://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/article-female-advisory-board-launches-peer-group-accelerate-growth-yorkshire-businesses)\n\n[](https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=Female%20Advisory%20Board%20launches%20peer%20group%20to%20accelerate%20growth%20of%20Yorkshire%20businesses&via=TheStartupsMag&url=https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/article-female-advisory-board-launches-peer-group-accelerate-growth-yorkshire-businesses)\n\n[](https://www.linkedin.com/cws/share?url=https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/article-female-advisory-board-launches-peer-group-accelerate-growth-yorkshire-businesses)\n\n[](https://wa.me/?text=Female%20Advisory%20Board%20launches%20peer%20group%20to%20accelerate%20growth%20of%20Yorkshire%20businesses%20https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/article-female-advisory-board-launches-peer-group-accelerate-growth-yorkshire-businesses)\n\n###### Read Next\n\n[![](https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/SM-Article-Photo-14-180x180.png)](https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/article-south-summit-extends-registration-deadline-madrid-startup-competition)\n\n##### [South Summit Extends Registration Deadline for Madrid Startup Competition](https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/article-south-summit-extends-registration-deadline-madrid-startup-competition \"Female Advisory Board launches peer group to accelerate growth of Yorkshire businesses\")\n\nFAB Enterprise is aimed at [female](https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/article-startup-magazines-20-most-influential-women)\\-led/owned businesses in Yorkshire heading into the eight-figure revenue bracket and onwards. With the addition of FAB Enterprise, there is now an eco-system of support for every stage of a business’ journey. FAB Grow is designed for smaller businesses with a turnover under £500k, and FAB Scale for those companies with a turnover exceeding £500k+, wanting to build and scale up.\n\nEstablished in September 2023 by Samantha Addy with just seven members, FAB has rapidly grown to 25 members from some of Yorkshire’s most successful female-led businesses. By April, FAB will have over 50 members with a combined turnover of more than £100 million, employing 500+ employees in the region, making a positive impact on the Yorkshire and UK economy and society as a whole.\n\nWithin FAB, business leaders come together to foster mutual growth, both professionally and personally, and find comfort from the often-solitary journey of [leadership](https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/article-art-balancing-leadership-and-management-startup), particularly for those occupying the upper levels of their respective industries.\n\nSamantha Addy, Founder and CEO of FAB, said: “FAB Enterprise is more than just a peer advisory group, it’s a transformative alliance where female leaders of multi-million-pound businesses can access the support, guidance, and collaboration they need to scale to the next level.\n\n“In the fast-paced and often isolating world of business leadership, having a trusted group of like-minded peers can make all the difference. FAB Enterprise provides a unique space for these exceptional women to invest in both their personal and professional growth, break through the challenges holding them back, and ultimately achieve greater success. Together, we’re redefining what it means to be a leader in today’s competitive landscape.”\n\nFAB has ambitious growth plans to hit c.£1 million turnover by the end of its second year, which will be achieved by creating additional regional boards and new board types to support more female leaders in Yorkshire. This ecosystem will be replicated across further regions in the UK.    \n\nSee Also\n\n[![](https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/SM-Article-Photo-1_0-180x180.png)](https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/article-dr-lisa-su-chair-and-ceo-amd-keynote-ces-2026-how-ai-changing-world)\n\n[News](https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/articles/news)\n\n###### [Dr. Lisa Su, Chair and CEO of AMD, to Keynote CES 2026 on how AI is Changing the World](https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/article-dr-lisa-su-chair-and-ceo-amd-keynote-ces-2026-how-ai-changing-world \"Dr. Lisa Su, Chair and CEO of AMD, to Keynote CES 2026 on how AI is Changing the World\")\n\nA peer advisory group is a collaborative, confidential network where business leaders or executives at similar levels come together to share experiences, solve challenges, and offer mutual support. These groups foster a trusted environment where members can openly discuss personal and professional issues, gaining insights, feedback, and advice from their peers. By leveraging the collective wisdom and diverse perspectives of the group, participants benefit from shared learning, problem-solving, and accountability, driving both personal growth and business success. The group also creates opportunities for networking and lasting connections, helping members tackle obstacles, refine strategies, and develop leadership skills in a supportive, results-oriented setting.\n\n_For more [startup news](https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/), check out the other articles on the website, and [subscribe](https://i.electronicspecifier.com/startupsmagazine) to the magazine for free. Listen to [The Cereal Entrepreneur](https://startups-magazine-the-cereal-entrepeneur.simplecast.com/) podcast for more interviews with entrepreneurs and big-hitters in the startup ecosystem._\n\n[0](https://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/article-female-advisory-board-launches-peer-group-accelerate-growth-yorkshire-businesses)\n\n[](https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=Female%20Advisory%20Board%20launches%20peer%20group%20to%20accelerate%20growth%20of%20Yorkshire%20businesses&via=TheStartupsMag&url=https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/article-female-advisory-board-launches-peer-group-accelerate-growth-yorkshire-businesses)\n\n[](https://www.linkedin.com/cws/share?url=https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/article-female-advisory-board-launches-peer-group-accelerate-growth-yorkshire-businesses)\n\n[](https://wa.me/?text=Female%20Advisory%20Board%20launches%20peer%20group%20to%20accelerate%20growth%20of%20Yorkshire%20businesses%20https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/article-female-advisory-board-launches-peer-group-accelerate-growth-yorkshire-businesses)\n\n Anna Wood February 3, 2025      \n\n0 Shares\n\n[Share 0](https://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/article-female-advisory-board-launches-peer-group-accelerate-growth-yorkshire-businesses)\n\n[Tweet](https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=Female%20Advisory%20Board%20launches%20peer%20group%20to%20accelerate%20growth%20of%20Yorkshire%20businesses&via=TheStartupsMag&url=https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/article-female-advisory-board-launches-peer-group-accelerate-growth-yorkshire-businesses)\n\n[Share](https://www.linkedin.com/cws/share?url=https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/article-female-advisory-board-launches-peer-group-accelerate-growth-yorkshire-businesses)\n\n[Share](https://wa.me/?text=Female%20Advisory%20Board%20launches%20peer%20group%20to%20accelerate%20growth%20of%20Yorkshire%20businesses%20https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/article-female-advisory-board-launches-peer-group-accelerate-growth-yorkshire-businesses)\n\nTrending Articles\n\n[![lone genius](https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/lone-genius-180x180.jpg)](https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/the-myth-of-the-lone-genius)\n\n###### [The myth of the lone genius](https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/the-myth-of-the-lone-genius \"The myth of the lone genius\")\n\n*   April 9, 2026\n*   4 mins Read\n*   0 Shares\n    \n    [](https://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/the-myth-of-the-lone-genius)[](https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=The%20myth%20of%20the%20lone%20genius&via=TheStartupsMag&url=https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/the-myth-of-the-lone-genius)[](https://www.linkedin.com/cws/share?url=https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/the-myth-of-the-lone-genius)[](https://pinterest.com/pin/create/bookmarklet/?url=https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/the-myth-of-the-lone-genius&media=https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/lone-genius.jpg)[](https://wa.me/?text=The%20myth%20of%20the%20lone%20genius%20https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/the-myth-of-the-lone-genius)[](mailto:?subject=The%20myth%20of%20the%20lone%20genius&body=The%20myth%20of%20the%20lone%20genius%20https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/the-myth-of-the-lone-genius)\n    \n\n[![IT crisis](https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/IT-crisis-180x180.jpg)](https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/the-hidden-it-crisis-inside-fast-growing-smes)\n\n###### [The hidden IT crisis inside fast-growing SMEs](https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/the-hidden-it-crisis-inside-fast-growing-smes \"The hidden IT crisis inside fast-growing SMEs\")\n\n*   April 9, 2026\n*   3 mins Read\n*   0 Shares\n    \n    [](https://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/the-hidden-it-crisis-inside-fast-growing-smes)[](https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=The%20hidden%20IT%20crisis%20inside%20fast-growing%20SMEs&via=TheStartupsMag&url=https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/the-hidden-it-crisis-inside-fast-growing-smes)[](https://www.linkedin.com/cws/share?url=https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/the-hidden-it-crisis-inside-fast-growing-smes)[](https://pinterest.com/pin/create/bookmarklet/?url=https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/the-hidden-it-crisis-inside-fast-growing-smes&media=https://startupsmagazine.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/IT-crisis.jpg)[](https://wa.me/?tex