      "content": "                         Empowering women in manufacturing and engineering | Tracy Brabin, Mayor of West Yorkshire posted on the topic | LinkedIn              \n\n  \n\nAgree & Join LinkedIn\n\nBy clicking Continue to join or sign in, you agree to LinkedIn’s [User Agreement](/legal/user-agreement?trk=linkedin-tc_auth-button_user-agreement), [Privacy Policy](/legal/privacy-policy?trk=linkedin-tc_auth-button_privacy-policy), and [Cookie Policy](/legal/cookie-policy?trk=linkedin-tc_auth-button_cookie-policy).\n\n[Skip to main content](#main-content)\n\n[LinkedIn](/?trk=public_post_nav-header-logo)\n\n*   [Top Content](https://www.linkedin.com/top-content?trk=public_post_guest_nav_menu_topContent)\n*   [People](https://www.linkedin.com/pub/dir/+/+?trk=public_post_guest_nav_menu_people)\n*   [Learning](https://www.linkedin.com/learning/search?trk=public_post_guest_nav_menu_learning)\n*   [Jobs](https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/search?trk=public_post_guest_nav_menu_jobs)\n*   [Games](https://www.linkedin.com/games?trk=public_post_guest_nav_menu_games)\n*   [Get the app](ms-windows-store://pdp/?ProductId=9WZDNCRFJ4Q7&mode=mini&cid=guest_nav_upsell&trk=public_post_guest_nav_menu_windows)\n\n[Sign in](https://www.linkedin.com/login?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww%2Elinkedin%2Ecom%2Fposts%2Fmayorofwy_were-committed-to-ensuring-that-more-women-activity-7346829071588229120-r0r9&fromSignIn=true&trk=public_post_nav-header-signin) [Join now](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww%2Elinkedin%2Ecom%2Fposts%2Fmayorofwy_were-committed-to-ensuring-that-more-women-activity-7346829071588229120-r0r9&trk=public_post_nav-header-join) [](https://www.linkedin.com/login?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww%2Elinkedin%2Ecom%2Fposts%2Fmayorofwy_were-committed-to-ensuring-that-more-women-activity-7346829071588229120-r0r9&fromSignIn=true&trk=public_post_nav-header-signin)\n\n [](https://uk.linkedin.com/company/mayorofwy?trk=public_post_feed-actor-image)\n\n[Tracy Brabin, Mayor of West Yorkshire](https://uk.linkedin.com/company/mayorofwy?trk=public_post_feed-actor-name)\n\n22,323 followers\n\n9mo Edited\n\n*   [Report this post](/uas/login?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fmayorofwy_were-committed-to-ensuring-that-more-women-activity-7346829071588229120-r0r9&trk=public_post_ellipsis-menu-semaphore-sign-in-redirect&guestReportContentType=POST&_f=guest-reporting)\n\nWe're committed to ensuring that more women have the opportunity to enter and thrive in our region’s manufacturing and engineering sectors, areas that are vital to innovation, sustainability, and growth. Our Women in Manufacturing and Engineering Network is a key part of this mission - connecting professionals, supporting career development, and challenging outdated stereotypes. Together, we're making West Yorkshire a place where ambition meets opportunity by breaking down barriers and building a more inclusive workforce.\n\n…more\n\n   [76](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww%2Elinkedin%2Ecom%2Fposts%2Fmayorofwy_were-committed-to-ensuring-that-more-women-activity-7346829071588229120-r0r9&trk=public_post_social-actions-reactions) [4 Comments](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww%2Elinkedin%2Ecom%2Fposts%2Fmayorofwy_were-committed-to-ensuring-that-more-women-activity-7346829071588229120-r0r9&trk=public_post_social-actions-comments)\n\n[Like](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww%2Elinkedin%2Ecom%2Fposts%2Fmayorofwy_were-committed-to-ensuring-that-more-women-activity-7346829071588229120-r0r9&trk=public_post_like-cta) [Comment](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww%2Elinkedin%2Ecom%2Fposts%2Fmayorofwy_were-committed-to-ensuring-that-more-women-activity-7346829071588229120-r0r9&trk=public_post_comment-cta)\n\nShare\n\n*   Copy\n*   LinkedIn\n*   Facebook\n*   X\n\nTranscript Transcript\n\n##### **Transcript**\n\nIf we want to achieve our goals for growth in the sector and the region as a whole, we absolutely need women. We had no women when I first started. We've now got women in the office. We've got the women in the workforce in the shop floor. And it's just to look to build upon that, create an atmosphere and a culture at work which actually supports women. There's still a lot of that stigma of it being a quite a a man's made world, you know, and I think it needs to be showcased and open that it's, it's. And just for men, we need women in this sector. This is the opportunity for growth and for new ideas circulate scale. But it is so much more normal now, refreshing to go into business and see women doing those technical roles rather than just in the traditionally female roles. Organizations that are diverse are more inevitable. They're more resilient to those economic shocks and more successful. Snow prejudice and you've to look around here today and you can see all the women from diverse backgrounds coming and making it happen. But one thing that has changed, which I think is really good is actually enabling the men, actually allowing the male workforce to take more time off of paternity leave work, more flexible hours. Then that allows the women to also enjoy those benefits. We cannot ship mindsets without men in the room. So thank you. Can we have a round of applause for all our allies in the loop?\n\n[](https://uk.linkedin.com/in/shahbanaziz?trk=public_post_comment_actor-image)\n\n[Shahban Aziz](https://uk.linkedin.com/in/shahbanaziz?trk=public_post_comment_actor-name)\n\nTCoE - Textile Centre of…•21K followers\n\n9mo\n\n*   [Report this comment](/uas/login?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fmayorofwy_were-committed-to-ensuring-that-more-women-activity-7346829071588229120-r0r9&trk=public_post_comment_ellipsis-menu-semaphore-sign-in-redirect&guestReportContentType=COMMENT&_f=guest-reporting)\n\nA fantastic launch event that I really enjoyed attending and took a lot back from - and looking forward to seeing the network go from strength to strength. Will be encouraging all our contacts to sign up.\n\n[\n\nLike\n\n](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww%2Elinkedin%2Ecom%2Fposts%2Fmayorofwy_were-committed-to-ensuring-that-more-women-activity-7346829071588229120-r0r9&trk=public_post_comment_like)[\n\nReply\n\n](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww%2Elinkedin%2Ecom%2Fposts%2Fmayorofwy_were-committed-to-ensuring-that-more-women-activity-7346829071588229120-r0r9&trk=public_post_comment_reply)[2 Reactions](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww%2Elinkedin%2Ecom%2Fposts%2Fmayorofwy_were-committed-to-ensuring-that-more-women-activity-7346829071588229120-r0r9&trk=public_post_comment_reactions) 3 Reactions\n\n[](https://uk.linkedin.com/in/jessicaaarmitage?trk=public_post_comment_actor-image)\n\n[Jessica Armitage](https://uk.linkedin.com/in/jessicaaarmitage?trk=public_post_comment_actor-name)\n\n1K followers\n\n9mo\n\n*   [Report this comment](/uas/login?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fmayorofwy_were-committed-to-ensuring-that-more-women-activity-7346829071588229120-r0r9&trk=public_post_comment_ellipsis-menu-semaphore-sign-in-redirect&guestReportContentType=COMMENT&_f=guest-reporting)\n\nLove to see this, a great overview of what we want to achieve from the Women in Manufacturing and Engineering network (WiMEN) 💥 [Catherine Darby-Roberts](https://uk.linkedin.com/in/catherine-darby-roberts?trk=public_post_comment-text), [Margaret Wood MBE](https://uk.linkedin.com/in/margaret-wood-mbe-05b82216?trk=public_post_comment-text), [Monta Fryer](https://uk.linkedin.com/in/monta-fryer-8a8a3b242?trk=public_post_comment-text), [Natalie Brewood](https://uk.linkedin.com/in/nataliebrewood?trk=public_post_comment-text) 👏 👏\n\n[\n\nLike\n\n](https://www.l