doors&trk=public_post-text) [#TogetherWeBuild](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fhashtag%2Ftogetherwebuild&trk=public_post-text)\n    \n      [27](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fenclos-corp_construction-inclusion-week-2025-activity-7383887399803817984-tTrM&trk=public_post_social-actions-reactions) [1 Comment](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fenclos-corp_construction-inclusion-week-2025-activity-7383887399803817984-tTrM&trk=public_post_social-actions-comments)\n    \n    [Like](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fenclos-corp_construction-inclusion-week-2025-activity-7383887399803817984-tTrM&trk=public_post_like-cta) [Comment](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fenclos-corp_construction-inclusion-week-2025-activity-7383887399803817984-tTrM&trk=public_post_comment-cta)\n    \n    Share\n    \n    *   Copy\n    *   LinkedIn\n    *   Facebook\n    *   X\n    \n    To view or add a comment, [sign in](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fenclos-corp_construction-inclusion-week-2025-activity-7383887399803817984-tTrM&trk=public_post_feed-cta-banner-cta)\n    \n\n![](https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D4E3DAQGlUj9EqHlZ8g/image-scale_191_1128/B4EZyy_5U4KIAg-/0/1772529621622/mayorofwy_cover?e=2147483647&v=beta&t=wXI_MZTkeGDWwSj1n24HyzJjU1GLmyY9wqM66lD5pzI)\n\n22,323 followers\n\n[View Profile](https://uk.linkedin.com/company/mayorofwy?trk=public_post_follow-view-profile) [Follow](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww%2Elinkedin%2Ecom%2Ffeed%2Fupdate%2Furn%3Ali%3Aactivity%3A7346829071588229120&trk=public_post_follow)\n\n## More from this author\n\n*    [